
Qualitative research with the objective of learning the care concept of the caregiver who is a member of the multiprofessional team working with hospitalized children with cancer. Fifteen pediatric caregivers from the Hospital de Cl√≠nicas de Porto Alegre took part of it. The data collected through semi-structured interviews have been submitted to content analysis. As to the theme category, Care Conception, caregivers regard care as Action, Tie, Presence, Feelings, and Promotion of personal and spiritual development.

